name: APP_OPENED
description: Tracked when a user session begins on the app or website.

name: USER_LOGOUT
description: Tracked when user Logout of the app/site or user reset.

name: PAGE_VIEWED
description: Tracked when a user visits a web page. Select page URL as event attribute to find number of users visiting a particular page or use it to setup a "Drop-off capture" Smart Trigger Web Push.

name: USER_MERGED
description: This event is tracked for a known user whenever a moengage user object is merged with it

name: UPDATE
description: Tracked when user updates the App.

name: INSTALL
description: Tracked when a user installs the app on the device.

name: Device Uninstall
description: Tracked when a user uninstalls the app on a device.

name: USER_REINSTALL
description: Tracked when a inactive user reinstalls the app on a device.

name: REINSTALL
description: Tracked when a user reinstalls the app on a device.

name: OPT_IN_BLOCKED
description: Tracked when a user denies to receive push notifications on Web.

name: WEB_OPTIN_ACCEPTED
description: Tracked when a user accepts the Push Permission Soft-ask on your website as part of the 2-step Push Opt-in mechanism.

name: CAMPAIGN_CONTROL_GROUP
description: Tracked when user is added to control group.

name: CAMPAIGN_USER_REMOVED_DUE_TO_CONTROL_GROUP
displayed_name: User removed from the campaign due to Control Group
description: Tracked when user is removed from the campaign due to control group.

name: CARD_CLICKED
description: Triggered when user clicks on a Card present in the App Inbox

name: CARD_DELIVERED
description: Tracked when card is sent to App Inbox after user clicks on App Inbox icon.

name: CARD_IMPRESSION
description: Tracked when card view happens.

name: CARD_INBOX_CLICKED
description: Tracked when user clicks on App Inbox icon.

name: EMAIL_CLICK
description: Tracked when a user clicks on any link in the email.

name: EMAIL_DEFERRED
description: Tracked when the receiving server delayed acceptance of the email message.

name: EMAIL_DELIVERED
description: Tracked when an email is delivered to the user.

name: EMAIL_DROPPED_UNSUBSCRIBE
description: Tracked when the email is dropped because user was already part of unsubscribe list.

name: EMAIL_HARD_BOUNCE
description: Tracked when our system finds an email is hard bounced. Typically happens when email adderss doesn't exist.

name: EMAIL_OPEN
description: Tracked when a user opens an email.

name: EMAIL_SENT
description: Tracked when our system sends email to a user.

name: EMAIL_SPAM
description: Tracked when a user marks the email as spam.

name: EMAIL_UNSUBSCRIBE
description: Tracked when a user unsubcribes from receiving emails.

name: EMAIL_VIB
description: Tracked when a user clicks on View in browser link present in the email.

name: FB_AUDIENCE_SYNC
description: Tracked when Facebook API returns 2xx response for add or delete request to an audience.

name: FLOW_TRIP_CONVERSION
description: Tracked when a user performs the conversion goal during their flow trip

name: IN_APP_AUTO_DISMISS
description: Tracked when a Mobile InApp Message is auto dismissed.

name: IN_APP_CLICKED
description: Tracked when a Mobile InApp Message is clicked by the user.

name: IN_APP_DISMISSED
description: Tracked when a Mobile InApp Message is closed by the user.

name: IN_APP_SHOWN
description: Tracked when a Mobile InApp Message is shown to the user.

name: ONSITE_MESSAGE_AUTO_DISMISS
description: Tracked when an On-site Messaging Campaign is auto dismissed.

name: ONSITE_MESSAGE_CLICKED
description: Tracked when an On-site Messaging Campaign is clicked by the user.

name: ONSITE_MESSAGE_DISMISSED
description: Tracked when an On-site Messaging Campaign is closed by the user.

name: ONSITE_MESSAGE_SHOWN
description: Tracked when an On-site Messaging Campaign is shown to the user.

name: SMS_CLICKED
description: Tracked when app/web link in SMS Campaign sent via MoEngage is clicked by user.

name: WEBP_MESSAGE_CLICKED
description: Tracked when a Web Personalization Campaign Message is clicked by the user.

name: WEBP_MESSAGE_DELIVERED
description: Tracked when a Web Personalization Campaign Message is delivered to the user.

name: WEBP_MESSAGE_SHOWN
description: Tracked when a Web Personalization Campaign Message is shown to the user.

name: WHATSAPP_DELIVERY_FAILED
description: Tracked when provider failed to send/deliver a WhatsApp Message for a user

name: MO_PUSH_PREFERENCE_CHANGED
description: Tracked when iOS device push preference is changed. It has the modified status.

name: NOTIFICATION_CLICKED_IOS
description: Tracked when a user clicks notification on iOS device.

name: NOTIFICATION_CLICKED
description: Tracked when a user clicks notification on Android device.

name: NOTIFICATION_CLICKED_WINDOWS
description: Tracked when a user clicks notification on Windows device.

name: NOTIFICATION_RECEIVED_IOS
description: Tracked when a user receives notification on iOS device.

name: NOTIFICATION_RECEIVED
description: Tracked when a user receives notification on Android device. It may take up to 12 hours for this event to be available in user profiles, for Segmentation and Analytics. There will be no delay for updating impressions in your campaign stats and for your Smart Trigger Campaigns to be triggered basis this event.

name: SMS_DELIVERED
description: Tracked when our system receives delivery receipt for the SMS sent to a user.

name: USER ENTERED FLOW
description: Tracked when a user falls in the target audience and has qualified for the entry in the Flow.

name: USER EXITED FLOW
description: Tracked when a user exits from a Stop Cell of the Flow.

name: n_c_s
description: Tracked when a notification is sent to the user as Cards campaign, doesn't indicate if the notification is received.
